t-prize-pool-structure/">Tournament prize pool structure</a>                         </li>                                              <li>                                                          <a href="/poker-software/updates/">Updates</a>                         </li>                                              <li>                                                          <a href="/poker-software/multi-flight-tournaments/">Multi flight tournaments</a>                         </li>                                       </ul>             </div>         </div>     </div> </div></div>               </div>      </div> </div></div>       </div>               </div>      </div> </div></div><?php include_once ($_SERVER["DOCUMENT_ROOT"]."/footer.php"); ?>